{"title":"我们的旗帜","authors":["赵长青"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":9,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵长青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望茫茫寰宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀与斧头托起的历史天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一颗巨星光芒四射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝视莽莽大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血与火洗礼的岁月长河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一座灯塔昼夜闪烁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大浪淘沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方显真金本色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨冲过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更见青松巍峨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七十五年栉风沐雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的旗帜更加鲜艳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七十多载千锤百炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的信念更加蓬勃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是因为——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒满真理的光泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数先烈的热血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在上面凝缩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千七百万优秀儿女的忠诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在上面镌刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二亿人民的意愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在上面寄托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从南湖红船举起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到点燃井冈山不熄的烽火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从遵义城楼凌空一展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到宝塔山下英才聚合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从西柏坡抖开锦绣前程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到中南海最英明的抉择"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的旗帜——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是走在队伍的前列"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是捧来硕硕战果……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在共和国的云天高高飘扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——永远不落"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}